      <title>墨西哥移民被杀案促使 Sheinbaum 誓言展开调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/mexico-s-military-kills-migrants-leading-sheinbaum-to-vow-to-investigate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·辛鲍姆承诺调查军方枪击一辆载有移民的卡车并导致六人死亡的事件。]]></description>
